metadata.name: Bumbee
metadata.description:
Holding a Honey Bee not only provides you a breathtaking artwork, but you're also available to:

Integrate your NFTs within the Metaverse
Stake your NFTs and earn daily coin rewards
Receive free NFTs from our next collections
            
On top of that, and the most important part, you’re directly assisting with the preservation of bees on planet Earth.
            
Honey Bee Club is paving a new way in the NFT space that’s showing the communities that there are ways to give back to the planet, a way to create benefits not only for yourself but also for the world we live in.
